Class GameDetailsAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.support.v7.widget.RecyclerView.Adapter<GameDetailsAdapter.GameViewHolder>
      • com.example.david.sdaproject.GameDetailsAdapter

  • public class GameDetailsAdapter
extends android.support.v7.widget.RecyclerView.Adapter<GameDetailsAdapter.GameViewHolder>
    DeveloperDetailsAdapter is an adapter that can provide the layout for each list based on a data source, which is a list of GameDetails objects.
